title: Japan to dispatch senior envoy to China, NHK says, as travel warning drives tourism selloff in Tokyo
summary: Japan's tourism-related stocks fell amid worsening diplomatic standoff between the two nations after Beijing issued a travel and study advisory.

title: Governors Awards Arrivals 2025: Ariana Grande, Jennifer Lopez and More Stars on the (Black) Carpet
summary: Tom Cruise, Debbie Allen, Wynn Thomas and Dolly Parton are being honored at the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences’ event, taking place Sunday night at the Ray Dolby Ballroom at Ovation Hollywood.
